id":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成個手術流程係點<br />\n會唔會滴麻醉<br />\n忍唔住想合埋眼會點<br />\n會唔會搵野夾住眼皮</blockquote><br />\n會先滴麻醉，跟住先望住部機嘅綠色點每邊眼大概1x秒左右，之後個部分會有眼撐支撐著，唔好鬥力聽醫生指示就OK"},{"pid":"b8210fb3c6c00a6bbef15692d6fce7cde46ab3fe","tid":393590,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:35:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反彈會點</blockquote><br />\n如果一年內反彈，佢包一次增進手術"},{"pid":"b26d5491a9e32fb1f53841246ef4a102c895990b","tid":393590,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:42:14.000Z","msg":"最嚴重後遺症係咪都係眼乾同埋眩光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c74a13dd06ce31b837ba3657bbce61f15836b01","tid":393590,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:47:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最嚴重後遺症係咪都係眼乾同埋眩光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係，不過都係因人而異"},{"pid":"5b5c8ff53781d9b5d9e0f82a207ffb1b5ca60deb","tid":393590,"uid":18635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:52:34.000Z","msg":"係邊間做呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5171354efc2e1f2411126aee47ad1eb5a3592914","tid":393590,"uid":88884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:56:07.000Z","msg":"我媽都叫我做 但我驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce3236fbffd5224a0a896f8ce0c970e648ac8eb","tid":393590,"uid":117868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:59:16.000Z","msg":"做完完全冇近視？"},{"pid":"16ce1a92751c513640b7af6abf46effef9318346","tid":393590,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:01:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最嚴重後遺症係咪都係眼乾同埋眩光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係，不過都係因人而異</blockquote><br />\n咁你依家有冇眼乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51bd22994ed7d65ac4a1cba995f7d5d1d8b7d280","tid":393590,"uid":5186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:05:28.000Z","msg":"做左一個月 日日訓4-5個鐘 眼都話好乾"},{"pid":"7fbdfe6831c19ac466b6db208da372aa44b3f8fe","tid":393590,"uid":5186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:05:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做左一個月 日日訓4-5個鐘 眼都話好乾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無話好乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fef0c528d4bfaaa77ec79707d94ca8b9b876c73","tid":393590,"uid":63440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:06:47.000Z","msg":"上過去聽講座 d眼科醫生自己都無做 你點睇"},{"pid":"1574bf4dda04683ca33a26997513ce8f70cbcc19","tid":393590,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:07:06.000Z","msg":"我早你5年前做 百幾度 無帶眼鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187c892fcabc867ae20819b6b8daf3e4903c261a","tid":393590,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上過去聽講座 d眼科醫生自己都無做 你點睇</blockquote><br />\n做左睇細節野會冇咁清<br />\n所以醫生冇做"},{"pid":"2160b1b11f226ae1badc6b478b130d8824cbdb52","tid":393590,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:11:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係邊間做呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香激"},{"pid":"8d268ced6bac2c78ae8e0840132f4b9548f481ee","tid":393590,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我早你5